// EmbeddedTerminal
// Thin wrapper that mounts an xterm.js terminal connected to a PTY session via WebSocket.
// Derives the WebSocket URL from the config and falls back to "default" if no session ID is provided.

FUNCTION EmbeddedTerminal(props) -> ReactNode                             EXPORT
  CALLS: XTermTerminal (XTermTerminal)
  Reads wsUrl from config.
  Uses provided sessionId or "default" as the terminal session identifier.
  Renders a flex container wrapping XTermTerminal with the resolved wsUrl and sessionId.
